data.description: Welcome to your new 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom corner lot ranch home situated in a prime Norfolk location! The kitchen was redone in 2019 with new Cabinets, Granite Countertops, and Stainless steel appliances. Bathrooms were renovated with matching cabinetry & granite countertops, newer laminate flooring throughout the home, New Windows & HVAC (2018), New Roof (2019), New Vapor Barrier (2023), and much more! All the Big Ticket items and heavy lifting have been completed. Home is turn-key ready for its next proud homeowners. This home offers the best of both worlds - a peaceful residential neighborhood and easy access to local amenities. Enjoy proximity to shopping, dining, parks, military bases, and schools. With the beach just a short drive away, you can embrace the coastal lifestyle.
